# Keep line endings deterministic across OS so build-time source parsers
# (e.g. scripts/seo-prerender.mjs splitting airdropData.ts on \n) behave the
# same on Windows checkouts as in Linux CI. Without this, a CRLF checkout made
# the prerenderer parse 0 airdrop projects locally.
* text=auto eol=lf
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.ico binary
*.webp binary
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary
